projectDetail: In our team, I specialized in frontend work with ChakraUI and React using Typescript. I created interactive pages, animations, and handled state management. I also collaborated on backend tasks, focusing on API integration and JWT token authentication, enriching the project's frontend
As the project lead for the frontend at Prime IT Club, I guided the team to success. With support from experienced seniors, we crafted the design using Tailwind, achieving our goals collaboratively
Crafted entirely by myself, my portfolio project was a joy to design and develop. Embracing research, I meticulously executed my vision, completing it as envisioned.

Tasked with bug fixes, new page creation, and enhancing sections on multiple pages for TechBall, I collaborated with a senior designer, resulting in a successful project. This journey with WordPress taught me invaluable lessons.
